MarketConditions --> MainArea : back
MarketReport --> MainArea : back
PestControlHelp --> PestControlTechniques : providePhoto
PestControlTechniques --> MainArea : back
SoilSuggestions --> MainArea : back
WeatherInsights --> MainArea : back
LabourAvailability --> MainArea : back

PestControlHelp --> PestControlTechniques : providePhoto

